body:
Hey guys,
Endertait here with my new episode of Fifa (Road to Div 1).
The quality is not great because i rendered it multiple times. I will fix that next episode.
Episode 1 has jump at the start i will fix that too. If you have any tips tell me bellow.
I am 1 subscriber away from 25 subscribers if you could please help me out i will make a 25 sub special.
Anyway here it is. (Soon will be heaps shorter parts)
Part 1:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xuA-6xyyIPA
Part 2:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KJiFiFHl_2g
Part 3:https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qkkkWUHad2g
Hope you enjoy and please comment, like or even SUBSCRIBE!
Thanks.
